article.description: — Isiaih Mosley had a career-high 31 points as Missouri State topped Alabama State 78-60 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Mosley carries Missouri St. past Alabama St. 78-60
article.linkText: Mosley carries Missouri St. past Alabama St. 78-60
article.story: SPRINGFIELD, Mo. -- — Isiaih Mosley had a career-high 31 points as Missouri State topped Alabama State 78-60 on Saturday night. Ja'Monta Black had 16 points for Missouri State (1-1). Gaige Prim added 11 points, 14 rebounds and five blocks. Donovan Clay had eight rebounds. Gerald Liddell had 14 points for the Hornets (0-3). Kenny Strawbridge added 12 points. Jordan O'Neal had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
